---
title: Smoky Chipotle Chicken with spiced potatoes and roast veg
description: Chipotle is an ingredient made of a smoke-dried jalapeno chilli, which gives it its spicy and smoky taste. In this dish, the smokiness in the chipotle-coated chicken is enhanced by the spiced potatoes and lightly charred veg.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/R16_W19_IE_IEXCLC0126-3_Main_high-b0039568.jpg
